<DIV>I blow away my pet's dps and did so before I entered the Elemental Planes and Time.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>So it depends on the level of play you are at. In Normal LDON&nbsp;our pets can easily off tank. In Hard LDON they're not very good.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>We get no AA's or Foci that help our pet's defensive abilities. The DPOC focus from LDON merchants provides an awesome regen effect to our pet when they are not in combat.</DIV>
